<span class="hl_keyword">lemma</span> Stop_unique [reuse]:<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;all-traces<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class="hl_operator">∀ </span>x #i #j<span class="hl_operator">.</span><br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="hl_operator">(</span><span class="hl_operator">(</span>Stop( x ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #j<span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">∧</span> <span class="hl_operator">(</span>Stop( x ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #i<span class="hl_operator">)</span><span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">⇒</span> <span class="hl_operator">(</span>#i <span class="hl_operator">=</span> #j<span class="hl_operator">)</span>&quot;<br/>
<a class="internal-link edit" href="/thy/trace/1/main/edit/Stop_unique">edit lemma</a>  or  <a class="internal-link delete" href="/thy/trace/1/main/delete/Stop_unique">delete lemma</a><br/>
